data.description: There's so much to love about this fabulous home in the heart of Springfield. From the inviting front porch, to its beautiful done over gorgeous kitchen! This 3-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom Cape, features a recently remodeled kitchen with spacious counters tops, beautiful cabinetry luxurious flooring etc. A large counter area with bar stools that flows into an open dining room with amazing sunlight. Entering an open living room with hardwood floors throughout leading to a wood fireplace. In the lower level, your lead to an absolutely to die for family room for move nights and so much more! Located upstairs is the master retreat offering a spacious private on-suite - with full bath & large walk-in closet. A fenced-in back yard, and a detached garage. A must see property!
